I used a railway app.


curl -X POST https://movies-api-production-9a50.up.railway.app/movies \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Accept: application/json" \
  -d '{"title":"Inception","director":"Christopher Nolan","year":2010}'




curl -L $URL/movies
